HEADWORD: Sance
<hw>S⟦eacute⟧`ance"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
L. <ets>sedens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>sedere</ets> to
